"									A map of <emphasis>&lt;String, Object&gt;</emphasis> corresponding to the settings to add. The change is ignored if the value of this field is empty." + 
"								</para>" + 
"							</listitem>" + 
"						</varlistentry>" + 
"					</variablelist>" + 
"					<example>" + 
